profile.bio: Graduated from MIT in 87, while there lived at TEP Xi.  Worked for DEC, Oak/Pixel Magic, ATI, Nauticus Networks, Sun, Pixtronix, Eta Devices, and, now, PodPonics. Lived in MA and now GA.
